 Sun . Apr . 21 Tucker not bad in No 7 Camp , but after have fed in Officer 's mess so long , it come rather hard . After Tea Georg Lawson and I went into Warminst and attend Evensong at Methodist Church and the Sing-Song and Bun Fight afterward . Attend Morn Servic at Sutton Veni Church . Bishop of Salisburi preach the Sermon . Mon . 22 Beauti day . Went on Parad , first time in 3 month . Went for slow walk with the Hut corpor and D.A.H.s . At night went to Warminst where I met " Pig " Johnson . Had a great old yarn . Tue . 23 Classif Day . Tobi ask to be mark A3 and " Von " will oblig him . Went into Warminst again and saw Johnson again . He belong to this district . Wed . 24 Some of the fellow got mail date March 18 . No bloomin ? mail for me yet , Can't understand it .
